Okay so I'm getting lazier and lazier with it as time goes on. I like to do it but it, like my homework, never seems to get completed. I guess it's a brain fuck or something like it. Life has been going slow, and it kinda sucks. I feel like I am getting a little paranoid, I feel like people don't really trust me. Maybe I'm going insaine. I guess that it will pass. 
Other wise things are going great. I got second in poetry over the whole state on last saturday and that helped my team to get fifth over all. Which owns because last year we were number 21 in the state; a whole 16 points plus the other five teams that went this year that werent there last year. I was sooo pumped.
We only have two more meets this year and then my high school career is over. Oh well, I can judge novie rounds next year and help out with the coaching.
I'll write more latter. Right now I have to actually do work while I'm in school.
Besides I have to go back to make out with that hottt Sara girl. I don't care if she is seeing anyone write now, he doesn't have to know. JK.
Peace,

Ryland

Well the play is done. That's nice, it has been fun but now I can actually relax for a while. Being done with it is a big accomplishment.

      Okay so thats a good thing. But my family sucks. You know how sometimes it's nice to be alone. Well for a while anyway. Now it's just annoying, because I have been home alone all freaken day. I'm begining to feel just a little antisocial, and lonely and enraged because I feel like a slave to this fucken house.

      I do have a problem with this one girl. I mean she's really cool but I don't have any interest in her. I think that she has a huge on me. I wish that I could just yell at her, "No I don't want to date you. Your friends are pushing me into it. I didn't want to date you in the first place. Besides I am sure that you will come to find me to be a dick head.  So your best choice to to find another fucken person. " But I can't do that because I don't want to hurt people. I have to big of a concentce (Spelled so wrong).

       The only person that I want to try to go out with is a freshman, named Serina. Me being a senior I don't think that that would go over to well in the pedifelia department of shit. GAAAAAAAH.

       I wish that I wasn't such an angry person. Ok so usually I'm content with the way that shit goes down, but once I am pissed off at a number of thing shit really hits the fan and I get royal pissed and want to rip the whole fucken world in half.

DHFGADSHFJKHADFSKGKJDSAHGFJKHFAGK,

Ryland
Forgot to enter how I got together with my band (Skraw) yesterday and did some serious ass kicking.

Oh yes. A day off. Sooo sweet. Well it really wasn't a day off. I was working durring the day on the school play. Infact I was working most of the day (from nine to four.) But I would much rather work on a play any day than attend that pain in the ass, up tight, hypocrite, Mrs. Brown's class. In any case I am in a good mood. I've been working hard and getting due respect for it. Besides my work is clearly visable on the stage.
     Wow I am hyper right now. I'm looking forward to tomorrow. I'm getting up early to go and do work on lighting and try to blind myself with the glory of electricity. Then I'm going to the diverstity team retreat. We will have fun all night, lots of girls. Oh yes. It will be enjoyable.
     I have gotten into one of those marraige at fourty things. Once I turn fourty and if I am not married or seeing anyone at that time than I am going to get married to one of my friends Shyla. Part of me is in love with her anyway and I haven't seen her in a long time and I really need to. In anycase not much else is up. Just keepin buisy and happy.

GRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRR I want to pull out my hair and yell fuck you at everything in my way! Why are some people sooo great in their minds that they think that they can boss us all around? Fuck them! I'm meen really...who died to make you king and queen shit?
